==Introduction== <!--T:9-->

<!--T:1-->
[[Assembly2 Workbench|Assembly2]] is an assembly workbench for FreeCAD v0.15 with support for importing parts from external files.

<!--T:10-->
As stated by its author [https://forum.freecadweb.org/viewtopic.php?f=17&t=16591 on the forum], it is no longer maintained since 2016, therefore it may have issues with FreeCAD 0.17 and above. The newer and actively maintained [[A2plus Workbench|A2plus Workbench]] is a good alternative.

